What you need to know:  The match was delayed by over half an hour due to security problems outside the ground that prevented many fans entering the stadium in time for kick-off.Brazilian winger Vinicius turned in Fede Valverde's enticing low cross in the 59th minute at the Stade de France and Liverpool could not find an equaliser as Jurgen Klopp's side lost to the Spanish giants in a Champions League final for the second time in five seasons.